  html += '    var DEFAULT_TEMPLATES = [{"id":"accept_a","label":"Accept + Confirm","text":"Hi {{diner_name}}! I would love to host your {{party_size}} person gathering on {{date}}. Everything looks great - I will prepare the menu we discussed. Looking forward to it!\\n\\nConfirm the booking and I will get started.\\n\\n- {{chef_name}}"},{"id":"accept_b","label":"Accept + Logistics","text":"Hi {{diner_name}}! Happy to confirm your {{party_size}} person booking for {{date}}. A few notes:\\n- Come to my kitchen at the address provided\\n- Payment will be handled through the platform\\n\\nReady when you are!\\n\\n- {{chef_name}}"},{"id":"decline","label":"Decline Politely","text":"Hi {{diner_name}}, thanks for reaching out! Unfortunately I am not available on {{date}}. I have really enjoyed hearing about your event - if your plans change or you would like to explore another date, please do not hesitate to reach out again.\\n\\nBest of luck with your event!\\n\\n- {{chef_name}}"},{"id":"more_info","label":"Request Info","text":"Hi {{diner_name}}! Your event sounds wonderful. Before I can confirm, I have a couple of quick questions:\\n- Do you have a preferred start time?\\n- Any dietary restrictions I should know about?\\n\\nLet me know and I will get back to you right away.\\n\\n- {{chef_name}}"},{"id":"counter_date","label":"Different Date","text":"Hi {{diner_name}}! I would love to host you, but {{date}} is not going to work for me. Could I offer you an alternate date instead? Everything else about your inquiry looks great.\\n\\nLet me know!\\n\\n- {{chef_name}}"}];\n';
  html += '    var currentTemplates = DEFAULT_TEMPLATES.slice();\n';
